# Applies only to builds whose `context:` is playground-v2/ (the host images —
# see hosts/Dockerfile). Services with scoped contexts (./keycloak, ./squid,
# ./unbound, ./zeek) have their own context roots and are unaffected.
#
# Host builds only need hosts/ + keycloak/realm.yaml. Everything else is noise.
*
!hosts/
!hosts/**
!keycloak/realm.yaml
